<title>习近平就缅甸遭受地震灾害向缅甸领导人敏昂莱致慰问电</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%B1%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E7%81%BE%E5%AE%B3%E5%90%91%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%8F%E6%98%82%E8%8E%B1%E8%87%B4%E6%85%B0%E9%97%AE%E7%94%B5</link>
